<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="statue base">base</rs> capital with heavy moulding above (top <measure type="length" dim="none">0.68</measure>   × <measure type="length" dim="none">0.70</measure>; shaft <measure type="length" dim="none">0.42</measure>   × <measure type="length" dim="none">0.37</measure>; height <measure type="depth" dim="none">0.32</measure>), broken away to right.</p>
